<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> without moulding or decoration, chipped along all edges and missing the lower right corner (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.14</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.265</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.55</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on one face, which is itself chipped approximately in the centre. Line 1 is very close to the upper edge, suggesting a composite monument.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Probably second century; well-cut in distinctive non-monumental forms, designed with a ruler and compass and cut with monumental techniques; lunate epsilon, sigma, omega; cursive feaures in alpha; ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΠΝ</foreign>, l.2, <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign> and <foreign lang="grc">ΗΜ</foreign> in l.4; ave. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.035</measure>
</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date exact="none" cert="low" notAfter="0200" notBefore="0101"> second century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)
</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="1"/> <w lemma="ἀθάνατος">ἀθανάτοισιν</w> <w lemma="ὅμοιος">ὅμοια</w> <w lemma="πόρω">πόρες</w> <w lemma="κλυτός">κλυτὰ</w> <w lemma="ἔργον">ἔργα</w> <w lemma="πόλις">πόληι</w> <g type="scroll"/> <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>  <lb n="2"/> <w lemma="ἥρως">ἥρως</w> <w lemma="εὐσεβής">εὐσεβίης</w> <w lemma="θεοτερπής">θεοτέρπεος</w> <w lemma="ἔμπνοος"><unclear reason="damage">ἔν</unclear>πνοος</w> <w lemma="εἰκών">εἰκών</w> <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>  <lb n="3"/> <w lemma="τοὔνεκα">τοὔνεκα</w> <w lemma="νῦν">νῦν</w> <w lemma="νάω">νάεις</w> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Εὐπείθιος">Εὐπείθιε</name></persName> <w lemma="καί">κα<unclear reason="damage">ὶ</unclear></w> <w lemma="πόλος">πόλον</w> <w lemma="ἄστρον">ἄστρων</w> <supplied reason="lost"><space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/></supplied>  <lb n="4"/> <w lemma="ψυχή">ψυχὴν</w> <w lemma="ἀναπνέω">ἀμπνεύσας</w> <w lemma="ὅτε">ὅτε</w> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Μάρτιος">Μαρτίο<unclear reason="damage">υ</unclear></name></persName>  <w lemma="ἦμαρ"><unclear reason="damage">ἦμαρ</unclear></w>  <w lemma="παίζω">ἔπαιζ<unclear reason="damage">ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied></w>  <lb n="5"/>  <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>    <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>    <space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>  </ab>
